item.title: Covid-19 Cases Analysis in Toronto
item.description: Abstract In this article, we investigated the covid-19 cases in Toronto. We want to demonstrate how covid-19 cases spread around Toronto, what age group has the highest number of cases, and the rate of severity in all cases, etc. Through analyzing the data from open data Toronto, we want to show people a comprehensive and detailed circumstances of this ongoing pandemic in Toronto. Introduction Do men or women more likely get infected by covid-19 in Toronto?
